${ingredientListBlock}${aiAutoInstruction}

AMOUNT CONSTRAINT: Each PANTRY ingredient must NOT exceed its stated amount. Extra protein ingredients (marked above) have NO amount cap — use as many grams as needed to hit the target.
You MAY add up to 3 optional flavor extras in a group "Optional add-ons" with optional=true and missing=true.
NEVER mark approved protein extras as optional or missing.

