${ingredientListBlock}

NO additional ingredients whatsoever. Every item in the recipe must come from this exact list. Do NOT add any oils, seasonings, aromatics, or other helper ingredients under any circumstances.`;

  // ── STRUCTURAL DISH REQUIREMENTS (HARD RULE) ─────────────────────────────────
  // Detect required structural ingredients from prompt and enforce them in output.
