/**
 * Build a strict, ingredient-accurate image prompt from the final validated recipe object.
 * 
 * Mode: STRICT — only visually represents required main ingredients.
 * Optional add-ons are NEVER shown in the image unless explicitly passed in allowedOptionals.
 * 
 * @param {object} recipe - final validated recipe object
 * @param {string[]} [allowedOptionals=[]] - optional add-on names explicitly allowed in image
