/**
 * DisplayLanguageSettings — Production-grade settings page.
 * 
 * - Full draft-state model: changes do NOT persist until Save
 * - Save button enabled only when there are unsaved changes
 * - Hydration gate: skeleton until backend prefs loaded (no flicker)
 * - Navigation guard: confirms leaving with unsaved changes
